# HTML & CSS Tags Demo 🌐🎨

This beginner-friendly project demonstrates the majority of **HTML and CSS tags** in real use. It's designed for students, developers, and educators who want a quick reference or learning tool.

## 🔧 Files Included

- `index.html` — A showcase of almost all HTML tags with examples.
- `style-tags.html` — Common CSS properties with live demonstrations.
- `styles.css` — Shared styling for clean and readable layout.

## 📸 Preview

![Preview](preview.png)

## 🚀 How to Use

1. Clone or download this repo.
2. Open `index.html` and `style-tags.html` in your browser.
3. Explore and learn interactively!

## 🤝 Contribute

Feel free to fork, clone, and improve. Pull requests are welcome!

